dct_description_sm: Publisher's number: 626. Includes 3 insets of Yuyuan Garden, Shanghai and region, and Hangkou Park (Lu Xun Park). Includes col. ill. "This map was created on an Apple Macintosh Centris 650. 70 megabytes of RAM was added along with a Radius PrecisionColor Pro 24x and a Math Chip. Adobe Illustrator 5.5 was used as the drawing software. An Abaton 300/colour scanner using Adobe Photoshop 2.5 was used to create the map templates from the manuscripts and to create the photographs.."
